title: 4K - The Passionate People Eater 1960 - The store with more. Feed the plant, or face the horror!

sources.title: 4K - The Passionate People Eater 1960 - The store with more. Feed the plant, or face the horror!
sources.description:
Seymour works in a skid row florist shop and is in love with his beautiful co-worker, Audrey. He creates a new plant that not only talks but cannot survive without human flesh and blood.

Original title: The Little Shop of Horrors (1960) 
B&W version: https://youtu.be/aZ2CuqGkHZ8

Film review: https://youtu.be/TxgybIkYsB0

Directed by Roger Corman
